groovyx.net.http

Class OkHttpBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • groovyx.net.http.HttpBuilder
      • groovyx.net.http.OkHttpBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class OkHttpBuilder
extends groovyx.net.http.HttpBuilder

    HttpBuilder implementation based on the OkHttp client library.

    Generally, this class should not be used directly, the preferred method of instantiation is via the groovyx.net.http.HttpBuilder.configure(java.util.function.Function) or groovyx.net.http.HttpBuilder.configure(java.util.function.Function, groovy.lang.Closure) methods.
